# Single source for agent instructions

Project-wide AI instructions are **only** in **`.claude/CLAUDE.md`**.

Repository root **`claude.md`** and **`AGENTS.md`** are **symbolic links** to that file (same bytes for Cursor, Claude Code, Codex-style tools).

**When editing:** change `.claude/CLAUDE.md` only. Do not replace the symlinks with separate copies of the markdown, or instructions will diverge again.
